Author: TheManyArchetypes
Text: When I over eat and feel really full/bloated I feel like my stomach is as big as it was 80lbs ago. I took a shower after eating more then I needed to yesterday, and got a little freaked out when I touched my stomach, and it wasn't taking up space the way I imagined it should.  I don't know, it's just a really surreal feeling when it happens. Like I'm me, but not me.

Author: nxhshchskbxn
Text: i don't have any advice but i completely relate and i know it can be so awful to deal with. i hate never knowing what's real. i wish i could just detach from my body for a minute and actually see myself as other people do. except then i'd probably want to kms lol
